This project predicts next-day stock price ranges for selected companies (e.g., AAPL, MSFT) using Yahoo Finance historical data and a Random Forest Regressor.

Features:

Downloads and preprocesses historical stock data via yfinance

Creates lag-based features for time-series forecasting

Trains and evaluates a Random Forest regression model

Predicts next-day price range in USD, EUR, and INR

Generates detailed performance reports (MSE, Accuracy)

Plots historical prices vs. predicted returns

Exports a formatted Word report with tables and charts

Libraries Used:
yfinance, numpy, pandas, scikit-learn, matplotlib, prettytable, python-docx

Intended Use:
For educational and experimental purposes. Not financial advice.
